  基于悬链线方程的系泊系统状态分析
  Based on the Catenary Equation Analysis of the Mooring System State
 
</article-title></title-group><contrib-group><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>郭</surname><given-names>迎雪</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff1"><sup>1</sup></xref><xref ref-type="corresp" rid="cor1"><sup>*</sup></xref></contrib><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>姚</surname><given-names>晴</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff3"><sup>3</sup></xref><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff2"><sup>2</sup></xref></contrib><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>樊</surname><given-names>懿锋</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff4"><sup>4</sup></xref><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff2"><sup>2</sup></xref></contrib><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>李</surname><given-names>宗军</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff5"><sup>5</sup></xref><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff2"><sup>2</sup></xref></contrib><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>范</surname><given-names>兴奎</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff5"><sup>5</sup></xref><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff2"><sup>2</sup></xref></contrib></contrib-group><aff id="aff4"><addr-line>青岛理工大学计算机工程学院，山东 青岛</addr-line></aff><aff id="aff3"><addr-line>青岛理工大学汽车与交通学院，山东 青岛</addr-line></aff><aff id="aff1"><addr-line>青岛理工大学机械工程学院，山东 青岛</addr-line></aff><aff id="aff5"><addr-line>青岛理工大学理学院，山东 青岛</addr-line></aff><aff id="aff2"><addr-line>null</addr-line></aff><author-notes><corresp id="cor1">* E-mail:<email>1392290558@qq.com(郭迎)</email>;</corresp></author-notes><pub-date pub-type="epub"><day>12</day><month>05</month><year>2017</year></pub-date><volume>06</volume><issue>03</issue><fpage>296</fpage><lpage>307</lpage><permissions><copyright-statement>&#169; Copyright  2014 by authors and Scientific Research Publishing Inc. </copyright-statement><copyright-year>2014<